
title Solution Architecture for CI/CD and Environment Isolation

Development {
  Dev Database [icon: aws-dynamodb]
}
Production {
  Prod Database [icon: aws-dynamodb]
}
CI CD Tools {
  Gitlab CI [icon: gitlab]
  Github Action [icon: github]
}
Deployment Target {
  Heroku [icon: heroku]
}

Gitlab CI > Development
Gitlab CI > Production
Github Action > Development
Github Action > Production
Development > Heroku
Production > Heroku
